  "title": "Low Code Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Primary Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Develop POC prototype using low-code platforms and rapid development methodologies</li>\n  <li>Implement user interface components for real-time transcription display and language selection</li>\n  <li>Create integration modules for audio and video source connectivity and transcription engine APIs</li>\n  <li>Build transcription history management and file storage and indexing functionality</li>\n  <li>Develop mobile-responsive web application components</li>\n  <li>Implement user authentication and access control mechanisms</li>\n  <li>Create automated testing frameworks and deployment pipelines for POC environment</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Required Experience and Qualifications</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proficiency in Microsoft Power Platform, OutSystems or similar enterprise low-code platforms</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years in low code development</li>\n  <li>Experience integrating with government systems and APIs within GCC environments</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of IM8 security requirements and implementation in low-code solutions</li>\n  <li>Understanding of real-time data processing and API integration methodologies</li>\n  <li>Experience with responsive web design and cross-platform compatibility</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with government development standards and coding practices</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of audio-visual system integration and multimedia processing</li>\n  <li>Experience with Singapore Government digital services and common technology stacks</li>\n  <li>Ability to work within government network restrictions and security protocols</li>\n</ul>",
